<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Dear friends, <o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"AR-SA" dir=3D"RTL" style=3D"font-famil=
y:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=C7=E1=CA=D1=CC=E3=C9 =C7=E1=DA=D1=C8=ED=C9=
 =C3=CF=E4=C7=E5</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Warm greetings to all of you! I=
 hope this finds you well and that the year of 2026 has begun in a good way=
 for you all!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I am writing today with an over=
all update on how we hope to set a direction for the future work of the Mag=
hreb Network. It is slightly longer e-mail so I hope that you will find tim=
e to read it all.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">As I have mentioned many times =
before, we have gone through a lot of internal changes at SweFOR and we hav=
e had a long wait to understand what our overall funding partnerships will =
look like going forward. We now, finally,
 have that clarity and we have a platform on which we can build our work fo=
r the next three years!
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">It has been somewhat of a frust=
rating wait and for all the patience that you have all showed in different =
ways =96 thank you! During this time, so much of our shared work has also d=
eveloped in lots of interesting and good
 ways, and today we have a range of very interesting projects and collabora=
tions that are running well thanks to the shared relationships and foundati=
ons we have in our network. It is a true pleasure to be in touch with many =
of you connected to these projects
 and collaborations, and also to be in touch when there are significant upd=
ates and life events. Many things have happened in the last years =96 peopl=
e have got new jobs, started new studies, got married, celebrated successes=
, and dealt with challenges and losses.
 In this way, our network is working very well and the foundation of our re=
lationships is strong!
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><br>
At the same time, what is also true is that we still need to determine the =
best way forward for our collective work in this network and how this can s=
erve us in the best possible way. Looking back to last year, we tried diffe=
rent versions of online meetings
 as we were waiting for the overall clarity on our partnership situation. I=
 think it is fair to say that these online meetings have had their ups and =
downs in terms of how useful they have felt. And when I last sent one of th=
ese longer updates to all of you
 with some questions about future desires for the online meetings, there we=
re very few responses.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">This leads us to where we go fr=
om here. We still have a strong foundation in our network, we have lots of =
interesting work taking place and we have the possibility to make clear pla=
ns for the future. What we need to figure
 out and understand is how to do our shared work in a way that best serves =
the interests and needs of all network members going forward.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Our process for figuring this o=
ut will be to contact you all individually to schedule calls which each of =
you. In these calls, what we hope to understand is:
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">1) Are you still interested in =
being part of the Maghreb network?
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">2) What work, initiatives, etc.=
, that you are currently involved in can be supported by the network?
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">3) What is the best format for =
this support going forward?
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">We will contact all of you =96 =
regardless of how much or little we have been in touch in this last year =
=96 and hope to get a chance to speak to everyone. It will be very importan=
t in order to determine our direction going
 forward. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">We will begin this process in t=
he coming days and hope to have it all finalized by the end of Ramadan, and=
 then be able to return to everyone with a clear set of priorities and a cl=
ear future direction for our shared
 work in this network. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">We look forward to speaking to =
you all in the coming weeks! Until then, wishing you all the very best.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">On behalf of the SweFOR team, <=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Erik<o:p></o:p></span></p>
